{
  "stem": "26728.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Left Frankfurt early in the morning and stopped and refueled someplace along the way-- I don't remember where-- which was not unusual.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Used to go to the bathroom and maybe get a sandwich or something and refuel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got to Munich about [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 11:30, 11:00, 11:30, 12:00, well, before noon.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were to be met by elements of the infantry units that-- and the tank units that had-- that were fighting in the area.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Radioed and were told not to try to land in Munich.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was still-- there was still fighting going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Turn around, go back to Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You can't land around here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the flight leader said, we're, we're-- our destination is Dachau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Can we get to Dachau?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Is-- and these guys talked on the radio, and we could hear them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and he mentioned some unit that was in Dachau that was-- that was at the gates of Dachau.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were-- they were in the camp, but the camp was out of control.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and-- but there were-- there were troops there, so we could-- we could communicate with the troops, and he-- and they, they patched us through and asked the troops to, to clear off a section of the road so we could land-- 600 feet minimum.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they put panels down, which was no problem.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went to-- from Munich to Dachau, and then the road was probably a mile or so away from the camp, so we flew over the camp.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it looked like a riot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We could-- you know, and we couldn't hear anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we landed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think there were about five airplanes.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
